profile:
At Ironshore Construction, we "Turn Houses Into Homes". 

We at Ironshore hold trust, integrity and customer satisfaction as the pillars of our company. Through these values, we aim to make each and every client interaction as stress-free and enjoyable as possible by offering confident solutions and expert advice. We are students of our crafts and stay up to date on yearly trends, new technologies and techniques to bring you the best quality.
diplomas: BSc Honours Kinesiology from McMaster University
warranty_terms: Yes. 2 Years Limited on Workmanship.  Plus respective manufacturer's warranty. Please ask for more details.
